New place opened in Gachibowli  ,Biryani was great ,very authentic and the portion size too was great, Telangana chicken with some rotis made my day.

The food here is Nice and hot.. according to my expectation. I have ordered here twice .. once kebabs and on other occasion.. Telangana chicken curry and biryani.. the biryani I had here was amazing and I couldn't decide which one I liked more.. the kebab or the biryani.. finger licking good...
The biryani is well cooked and has a consistent taste till the last spoon. The quantity was very very healthy.
Please maintain this quality and quantity of the biryani..

As mentioned by a few people, the packaging is very good.
Food Taste: Food was impressive, especially Punjabi Chicken (Curry) if you like the dhaba style chicken.
Chicken Tikka was fresh & succulent, and the best one to me was Krackjack Chicken (Must Try)

I orded a Biryaani from here today.. It was chicken dum Biryaani
On packaging I can give it 3.5/5 star it was proper.
Now coming on the taste ... I will sincerely ask the restaurant management please taste it.. And let me know if you find any taste in it.. Biryaani is all about flavor and all I can taste is white rice which was I think from leftover it was very hard and dried out... Even the chicken was not properly cooked in dum.. The masala that holds the chicken was even taste raw.. And uncooked.
I was gonna complained about the quantity which we get in 300 bucks but thank god it was not that much... We would have to through it out.. Cuz the things is I don't like to waste food.
Please do taste your Biryaani... And improve.
Best wishes
